sample printing of my ideas then talk to VVA about them putting it on their web site. <br><br>
 All monies gained from this, if any are to be shared between the VVA &amp; supporting this site. I have three investors who are willing to back me with a few $$$ just becasue they like the idea and it comes off the taxes...<br><br>
We'll see where it goes from there, maybe no where at all<br>
BUT that should NOT stop those of you out there who sit in front of a PC wondering what to do with youself. CREATE YOU OWN PERSONAL CARDS ! The birthday cards my kids made for me just by drawing on some paper, creating their own happy whatever cards carry a lot of weight with yours truly... <br><br>
